      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Woman's club is closing the\nseason until autumn after the most\nsuccessful year of work it has yet\nhad. The organization has reach\ned membership of Ito, with the\ndifferent departments efficiently\norganized yesterday afternoon\nwas devoted to a demonstration by\nthe household economics depart\nment under direction of Miss Chris\ntine Riis at the high school. Mem\nbers of the class served invited\nfriends with a banquet of their\npreparation and the occasion was\na success socially and scientifically.\nThis ends the departments work\nfor the summer The last meet\ning of the current topics and\nliterary department will be held\nnext Thursday at 2 p. m. at the\nchamber of commerce, and the So\ncial economics department closes\nFriday afternoon at the same hour\nand place. The French and Ger\nman classes will meet as usual."
    }
